    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beneath Eonpolis, The Everlasting City, lies a long-forgotten secret. One that maintains the city as if it were magic, one that is meant to last forever, until one day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Eonheart, an enigmatic machine complex that sustains an entire city by itself, in this classic-style 2D Puzzle Platformer, and unearth lost secrets... and unseen terror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115410/extras/c0af04babfaa102e590d3916d325538b.webp?t=1760537446\" width=606 height=33 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A platformer where YOU get to decide the platforms!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using a mysterious wrench found inside Eonheart, you can create various blocks, each with a unique ability and many interactions. Use them to your advantage to traverse halls of machinery, brave hazardous chambers, and discover the secrets of The Everlasting City!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115410/extras/7e20460035a45f5e497e9bbbf46c19dd.poster.avif?t=1760537446\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115410/extras/7e20460035a45f5e497e9bbbf46c19dd.webm?t=1760537446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115410/extras/7e20460035a45f5e497e9bbbf46c19dd.mp4?t=1760537446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Puzzle, with a side of action?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 chambers of Eonheart are full of enigmatic mechanisms waiting to be solved. Manipulate blocks and the environment and discover devious ways to traverse every nook and cranny! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, not all challenges come in the same form. A hidden danger, unbeknownst to the people of Eonpolis, awaits you. Can you use your knowledge in the most critical situations and take down even the most terrifying foes?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115410/extras/5e7f921abbb457e6f8a1e4f2e4852fa7.poster.avif?t=1760537446\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115410/extras/5e7f921abbb457e6f8a1e4f2e4852fa7.webm?t=1760537446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115410/extras/5e7f921abbb457e6f8a1e4f2e4852fa7.mp4?t=1760537446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover a place lost to history</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eonheart contains many unique areas, each with its unique environment, atmosphere, and mechanisms. From the machine-filled halls of Outer Hull to the searing hot conveyor lines of The Foundry, to the mysterious experimental Greenhouse, and beyond! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115410/extras/c3baa33864a1bbd81725d266fa7185ad.poster.avif?t=1760537446\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115410/extras/c3baa33864a1bbd81725d266fa7185ad.webm?t=1760537446\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115410/extras/c3baa33864a1bbd81725d266fa7185ad.mp4?t=1760537446\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Secrets hidden from most eyes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Further secrets wait to be discovered off the beaten path. Whether behind the most obscure gates or unimaginable challenges, do you have what it takes to uncover them all and learn the whole story behind Eonheart?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115410/extras/c0af04babfaa102e590d3916d325538b.webp?t=1760537446\" width=606 height=33 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Seems like nothing lasts forever, after all.</i></p>",
